clusterProperties.name: otel.baggage.trace.attributes
clusterProperties.description: Baggage keys that create custom trace attribute that will be added globally to the server-kind span. Use * for all keys. eg. key1,key2

clusterProperties.name: otel.metricPrefix
clusterProperties.description: Open Telemetry metric prefix. Requires Gateway restart.

clusterProperties.name: otel.serviceMetricEnabled
clusterProperties.description: Enable Open Telemetry Service Metric. Requires Gateway restart.

clusterProperties.name: otel.trace.attributes
clusterProperties.description: Open Telemetry custom trace attributes that will be added globally to the server kind span representing the service in a trace at the end of policy processing. Supports context variable resolution. e.g. attr1=value1,attr2=${value2}
